伊朗總統阿曼尼內賈德（[Mahmoud
Ahmadinejad](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mahmoud_Ahmadinejad
"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mahmoud_Ahmadinejad")）於9月23日在美國紐約聯合國大會[演講](http://www.cnn.com/2009/POLITICS/09/23/general.assembly.ahmadinejad/
"http://www.cnn.com/2009/POLITICS/09/23/general.assembly.ahmadinejad/")時，反對伊朗政府及官方[侵害人權](http://www.iranhumanrights.org/2009/09/report09/
"http://www.iranhumanrights.org/2009/09/report09/")的抗議民眾信守[承諾](https://globalvoicesonline.org/2009/09/23/iran-
protests-to-welcome-ahmadinejad-in-new-york/
"https://globalvoicesonline.org/2009/09/23/iran-protests-to-welcome-
ahmadinejad-in-new-
york/")，在場外[聚集示威](http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/babylonbeyond/2009/09/iran-
protesters-at-the-united-nations-decry-ahmadinejad.html
"http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/babylonbeyond/2009/09/iran-protesters-at-the-
united-nations-decry-
ahmadinejad.html")，抗議群眾[來自](http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-
dyn/content/article/2009/09/23/AR2009092305209.html?hpid=topnews
"http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-
dyn/content/article/2009/09/23/AR2009092305209.html?hpid=topnews")世界各地，包括加拿大、日本、伊朗等，伊朗在野陣營（又稱「綠色運動」）[也有許多代表出席](http://i37.tinypic.com/33lzed3.jpg
"http://i37.tinypic.com/33lzed3.jpg")。

YouTube網站上有許多記錄現場狀況的影片，例如以下幾段：

